| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0818 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a86f8ab-2c59-5d2b-afdf-2e2b084abeb0"
